================================================================================
USAGE & COMPLIANCE
================================================================================

Synnoesis orchestrates Anthropic's Claude using YOUR OWN credentials. It bundles
no API keys and grants no Claude access of its own. Your use of Claude is
governed by your own agreement with Anthropic, not by this project.

You are responsible for complying with Anthropic's terms:

  * Personal / single-user use: a Claude subscription via the official Claude
    CLI is permitted.

  * Serving other people or customers (multi-user / commercial-facing): you must
    use your OWN Anthropic API key under Anthropic's Commercial Terms -- NOT a
    personal subscription. Routing other users' requests through personal
    subscription credentials violates Anthropic's terms.

  * Review Anthropic's Consumer Terms, Commercial Terms, and Usage Policy before
    deploying: https://www.anthropic.com/legal

Commercial use of Synnoesis itself is permitted under the Apache License 2.0 --
just bring your own keys and protect yourself.

